    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <strong>Drag Racing 3D: Streets 2<br>The best sports &quot;drag racing simulator&quot; with big possibilities for tuning your car.   </strong> <br><br> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A FRESH APPROACH TO CUSTOMIZING YOUR CAR</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/8ee800ad0d36a8d82ed164f6a3444299.poster.avif?t=1759190772\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/8ee800ad0d36a8d82ed164f6a3444299.webm?t=1759190772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/8ee800ad0d36a8d82ed164f6a3444299.mp4?t=1759190772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Flexibility of settings, their quantity, and each one affects some parameter. <br>Create your car with style and increase its efficiency in competitions. <br> <br>⠀ <br><strong>COMPETE FOR THE CHAMPION TITLE WITH PLAYERS FROM ALL OVER THE WORLD</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/37983102ca084eac4c85feb1a7ade24d.poster.avif?t=1759190772\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/37983102ca084eac4c85feb1a7ade24d.webm?t=1759190772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/37983102ca084eac4c85feb1a7ade24d.mp4?t=1759190772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Lots of game modes: Classic race, time trial, tournament, or championship. <br>Want to be the best in one thing or take all the champion titles at once? – Show who’s the best here. <br> <br>⠀ <br><strong>EXTENSIVE CAR DEALERSHIP</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/6b49c52dc844b2b569d9b417329dcff1.poster.avif?t=1759190772\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/6b49c52dc844b2b569d9b417329dcff1.webm?t=1759190772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/6b49c52dc844b2b569d9b417329dcff1.mp4?t=1759190772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The game features more than 50 different models. We are constantly expanding the list of new cars. Replenish your collection by purchasing new cars. <br>⠀ <br><br><strong>MAKE FRIENDSHIP WITH OTHER PLAYERS</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/60a6bd8d40721a8aeaf4ce59e9c766b6.poster.avif?t=1759190772\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/60a6bd8d40721a8aeaf4ce59e9c766b6.webm?t=1759190772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/60a6bd8d40721a8aeaf4ce59e9c766b6.mp4?t=1759190772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Find new friends, create your own car club, and take part in team-vs-team races. <br>Choose your name, logo, color, and join team tournaments. <br> <br>⠀ <br><strong>MULTIPLE REWARDS</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/3ca90a16cf68570f33f23adcbc2e50c5.poster.avif?t=1759190772\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/3ca90a16cf68570f33f23adcbc2e50c5.webm?t=1759190772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249600/extras/3ca90a16cf68570f33f23adcbc2e50c5.mp4?t=1759190772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Daily rewards:</strong> Just log into the game and claim your prize.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blitz and Sprint:</strong> Complete daily missions that will earn you lots of in-game currency and experience.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scrapyard:</strong> Are you an experienced racer and know your cars? Then complete tasks collecting cars for the mechanic and earn reputation.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Marketplace:</strong> Freely set any prices for your items, and buyers can bargain.</p></li></ul>",
